  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Battle your way through 16 unique levels!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/052249b9ccc2878a82674d74186b5695.poster.avif?t=1764522470\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/052249b9ccc2878a82674d74186b5695.webm?t=1764522470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/052249b9ccc2878a82674d74186b5695.mp4?t=1764522470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight your way across high mountains, forest paths, deep caves, graveyards, spooky towns, and even Santa's toy factory. Experience 16 levels in total, all set within Christmas and Halloween themes.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Massive Variety of Weapons - Find Your Favorites!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/2f3988b82b1aa18ace6bf804cf75a163.poster.avif?t=1764522470\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/2f3988b82b1aa18ace6bf804cf75a163.webm?t=1764522470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/2f3988b82b1aa18ace6bf804cf75a163.mp4?t=1764522470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from a wide selection of firearms and melee weapons found in gift boxes. From lighter options like assault rifles and shotguns to heavy hitters like miniguns, rocket launchers, and flamethrowers, there's something for everyone.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Laid-Back SOLO or CO-OP Action</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/1be504b5715bfb70c6bfbd2b436381e7.poster.avif?t=1764522470\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/1be504b5715bfb70c6bfbd2b436381e7.webm?t=1764522470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/1be504b5715bfb70c6bfbd2b436381e7.mp4?t=1764522470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s always more fun to play together! Relax on the couch, grab a controller, and team up with a friend to battle Krampus's minions. While the game is fully playable in single-player mode, having a companion makes things easier and even more enjoyable. This game supports local couch co-op and Steam Remote Play Together but does not feature an online multiplayer mode.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tons of Enemies and Bosses</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/8094e294c58dcb2e2144cf9cddb31a54.poster.avif?t=1764522470\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/8094e294c58dcb2e2144cf9cddb31a54.webm?t=1764522470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/8094e294c58dcb2e2144cf9cddb31a54.mp4?t=1764522470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level introduces new enemy types and culminates in a unique boss fight. Encounter them, discover their weaknesses, and take them down!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Seasonal Updates</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/9f6b5ddf346bb17e2a20b73c2b21b0b9.poster.avif?t=1764522470\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/9f6b5ddf346bb17e2a20b73c2b21b0b9.webm?t=1764522470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/9f6b5ddf346bb17e2a20b73c2b21b0b9.mp4?t=1764522470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Christmas may be over, but the battle between Santa and Krampus rages on! Enjoy free content updates for the summer and Halloween seasons, with even more exciting additions on the way.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tested on Steam Deck</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/75dafa2a63ff437ca03cc98626179df8.poster.avif?t=1764522470\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/75dafa2a63ff437ca03cc98626179df8.webm?t=1764522470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/75dafa2a63ff437ca03cc98626179df8.mp4?t=1764522470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game runs perfectly on handheld devices! What’s better than a relaxing shootout to pass the time while you’re on the go?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Battle your way through 16 unique levels!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/052249b9ccc2878a82674d74186b5695.poster.avif?t=1764522470\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/052249b9ccc2878a82674d74186b5695.webm?t=1764522470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/052249b9ccc2878a82674d74186b5695.mp4?t=1764522470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight your way across high mountains, forest paths, deep caves, graveyards, spooky towns, and even Santa's toy factory. Experience 16 levels in total, all set within Christmas and Halloween themes.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Massive Variety of Weapons - Find Your Favorites!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/2f3988b82b1aa18ace6bf804cf75a163.poster.avif?t=1764522470\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/2f3988b82b1aa18ace6bf804cf75a163.webm?t=1764522470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/2f3988b82b1aa18ace6bf804cf75a163.mp4?t=1764522470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from a wide selection of firearms and melee weapons found in gift boxes. From lighter options like assault rifles and shotguns to heavy hitters like miniguns, rocket launchers, and flamethrowers, there's something for everyone.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Laid-Back SOLO or CO